 **Instead of `Task.Run`** — use `await` directly or `Task.Yield`:

 ```csharp
 // Yield to let renderer paint, then continue on sync context
 private async Task StartLongOperation()
 {
     status = "Starting...";
     await Task.Yield();
     await LongOperationService.RunAsync();
     status = "Done!";
